oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Songwriter Session - Cory Batten and Kent Blazy - 2018-02-17
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performances by singer songwriters Cory Batten and Kent Blazy in the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on February 17, 2018.
